
// This Hyperlambda snippet uses the [lt] slot to compare the number of tokens consumed by the text in [.context] with the integer value 4000. If the token count is less than 4000, the condition evaluates to true. The [openai.tokenize] slot calculates the token usage of the specified text, ensuring it doesn't exceed the OpenAI token limit.
lt
   openai.tokenize:x:@.context
   .:int:4000
